	   <tr><td colspan=2>Fear should NOT be used to reduce an amount of pulls, more than likely all it will do, is cause the mob to run and bring back more of it's kind or others that aggro with it to attack and kill you.&nbsp;&nbsp;Also, before using divine aura, which has a fairly fast cast time, you should build up your aggro with the mobs so that they continue to wail on you while Divine Aura is in place, thus reducing the damage taken by your tanks.<br><br>Gedran<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
