	   <tr><td colspan=2>Here's a tip for dwarves up until level 5 or so. if you kill skellies than you save up their bone chips and go to the paladins guild. Go past the altar and there will be a lone NPC on the left wearing patchwork and chainmail (I've forgotten his name) who will talk to you about the skeleton quest. Hold down CTRL and click on your bone chips, and put one bone chip in each 'give' slot. As you reward you receive some patchwork armor, some money and almost a bar of exp! Not bad for a level2 hey? later on he gives you rusty weapons which you can sell or use. Very handy.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
