	   <tr><td colspan=2>Greetings!!<br>Soloing as a cleric can be tough, Even tougher in Rallos Zek, as there are many who will try to interrupt you and take your hard earned coppers!<br><br>From lvl 1 to 5, it is very simple, stay in Newbie zone outside Kaladim, kill everything that moves, and SAVE ALL BONECHIPS!!<br>There is an NPC in the paladin guild that gives you an item, some cash, and real good xp for every 4 bonechips..this quest works great up to lvl 7, and decent up to 9<br>I never had to buy a bag, goblin whelps will drop one every now and then.<br><br>One key: Buff everyone you meet, it pays in the end to build up goodwill now, Especially on Rallos<br><br>Once you are lvl 5, move on to the dwarf skellies at the druid ring, you can solo all of these, pulling one at a time with your cool new undead nuke, rotating thru the three at ring and the one over the hill behind you..by the time you kill the fourth, yyou have just enough time to rest up before the one you killed first spawns again!!!<br><br>And that my friends, is all it takes to get to level 9, I will post again for 9 to 14 when I do it, but my plan is mainly chessboard..<br>&nbsp;<br>Senoj D'spair<br>Mistress of Dark Arts<br>Officer of Feral Elegance<br>Rallos Zek server<br></td></tr>
