	   <tr><td colspan=2>if you are gonna be a cleric you need to decide on a race...i am a dwarf cleric and i love him in my opinion dwarves are the best clerics cause they have good wisdom and STR to wear the plate like armor they are allowed to wear.&nbsp;&nbsp;Also pump all points into wisdom and the rest into STR or AGI.  Careful when you heal cause sometimes when the player is real low on hp and youheal  the mob sometimes attacks you.  Also if you can heal for lets say 25hp and someone is 5hp down in health do NOT heal him yet cause if you keep wasting mana healing  that 5hp then you wont  have enough to heal when you need it most also it wastes mana if you heal their missing 5hp with a 25hp heal.  Also i recomend you keep 1h and 2h blunt up in skill...mostly 1h blunt but keep 2h blunt decent in skill cause some nice priest 2h blunts are coming from kunark now.  these are some general tips nothing special.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
