	   <tr><td colspan=2>What has been said in all the posts below is true.&nbsp;&nbsp;Clerics are healers 1st and formost.  Many a time I've helped save people because they got into a fight and then suddenly were outgunned when 2 or 3 other things joined in.  I've helped save people that I've come across and usually they are thankful.  Even if you don't get xp you do get practice in your skills, such as alteration and the like.  The better you get at casting the less often you'll be interupted while casting and the more powerful they will get.<br><br>Yes you can go on the offensive but after a time why?  You get xp in a group weither you kill or not.  You'll live longer when you heal the group since you can do it faster for them than them waiting for it to come back. I'm only lv 2 so I really can't say what to do in the higher lvs but when I do know, I'll be back to post.<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br>Darien Targent<br>Cleric of the Light</td></tr>
